<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1437,311,652]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
This species has been previously confused with 
<taxonomicName authority="Linnaeus, 1758" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1758" box="[767,1180,506,532]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Pomacentridae" genus="Chromis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="chromis">
<emphasis box="[767,968,506,531]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Chromis chromis</emphasis>
(Linnaeus, 
<number box="[1109,1171,506,532]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="1758.0">1758</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
, e.g. by 
<bibRefCitation author="Maul" box="[1281,1431,506,532]" pageId="15" pageNumber="25" refString="Maul, G. E. (1949) Lista sistematica dos peixes assinalados nos mares da Madeira e indice alfabetico. pp 135 - 159. In: A. C. de Noronha &amp; A. A. Sarmento (1949) Vertebrados da Madeira, 2 º Volume-Peixes. Junta Geral do Distrito Autonomo do Funchal." type="book" year="1949">
Maul (
<number box="[1359,1422,506,532]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="1949.0">1949</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Nunes" box="[151,364,546,572]" pageId="15" pageNumber="25" refString="Nunes, A. A. (1974) Peixes da Madeira. Junta Geral do Distrito Autonomo, Funchal. 284 pp." type="book" year="1974">
Nunes (
<number box="[244,308,546,572]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="1974.0">1974</number>
: 
<number box="[322,355,546,572]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="79.0">79</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, and by Lloris &amp; Rucabado in 
<bibRefCitation author="Quero" box="[742,969,546,572]" pageId="15" pageNumber="25" refString="Quero, J. C., Hureau, J. C., Karrer, C., Post, A. &amp; Saldanha, L. (1990) Check-list of the fishes of the eastern tropical Atlantic. 3 volumes. Lisbon." type="book chapter" year="1990">
Quéro 
<emphasis box="[825,886,546,571]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">et al.</emphasis>
(
<number box="[905,969,546,572]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="1990.0">1990</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<number box="[982,1084,546,572]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="846.5" valueMax="847.0" valueMin="846.0">846-847</number>
), who include an (erroneous) record of the species from Madeira by 
<bibRefCitation author="Fowler" box="[603,775,586,612]" pageId="15" pageNumber="24" refString="Fowler, H. W. (1936) The marine fishes of West Africa based on the collection of the American Museum Congo expedition, 1909 - 1915. Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History, 70 (1 - 2), Part 1, 1 - 605; part 2, 607 - 1493." type="journal article" year="1936">
Fowler (
<number box="[702,766,586,612]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="1936.0">1936</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. See Domingues 
<emphasis box="[976,1034,586,611]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">et al.</emphasis>
(
<number box="[1050,1112,586,612]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="2005.0">2005</number>
) for a genetic study of eastern Atlantic and Mediterranean 
<taxonomicName box="[525,625,626,651]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Pomacentridae" genus="Chromis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[525,625,626,651]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Chromis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species.
</paragraph>
